for in循环

可以利用区间运算符
for index in 0...5 {
  print(index)
}
//输出： 0 1 2 3 4 5


stride函数：可变步长类型值的序列

stride(from:to:by)，开区间处理，最后一个值严格小于最大值；
stride(from:through:by)，闭区间处理，最后一个值小于或等于最大值；
.reversed(): 反向

for index in stride(from: 0, to: 10, by: 2) {
    print(index) 
} // 0 2 4 6 8

for index in stride(from: 0, through: 10, by: 2) {
    print(index)
} // 0 2 4 6 8 10

for index in stride(from: 0, to: 10, by: 2).reversed(){
    print(index)
} // 8 6 4 2 0



